{"word":"Jehoram","slug":"jehoram","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jehoram</b> <a href=\"#/H3088\">H3088</a> <br/> 1. King of Judah<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=50'>1Ki 22:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=16'>2Ki 8:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=3&verse=11'>1Ch 3:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=5'>2Ch 21:5</a> <br/> - Ancestor of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=8'>Mat 1:8</a> <br/> - Marries Athaliah, whose wicked counsels influence his reign for evil<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=19'>2Ki 8:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=13'>2Ch 21:13</a> <br/> - Slays his brothers to strengthen himself in his sovereignty<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=4'>2Ch 21:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=13'>2Ch 21:13</a> <br/> - Edom revolts from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=22'>2Ki 8:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=10'>2Ch 21:10</a> <br/> - Philistines and Arabians invade his territory<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=17'>2Ch 21:17</a> <br/> - Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=20'>2Ch 21:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=24'>2Ki 8:24</a> <br/> - Prophecy concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=21&verse=15'>2Ch 21:15</a> <br/> 2. A son of Ahab<br/> <a href='S:Joram'>Joram</a><br/> 3. A priest commissioned to go through Israel and instruct the people in the law<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=17&verse=8'>2Ch 17:8</a>"}]}